episodes.title: Inside the Spiritual Coaching Grift: Cult Tactics Disguised as Healing & Empowerment
episodes.description:
Spiritual coaching scams are everywhere. Glossy marketing wrapped in healing and empowerment, but built on cult tactics and manipulation. In this video, I expose the spiritual coaching grift: how it works, the red flags to watch for, and why real transformation can’t be sold through shame, secrecy, or subscription traps.

After falling for the hype myself, I learned how to tell the difference between real guidance and spiritual marketing that keeps you dependent.

You’ll learn:
✨ The cult tactics hiding inside spiritual coaching “containers”
✨ Why charging for spirituality isn’t the problem... dependency is
✨ How unfair advantage fuels the myth of “overnight success”
✨ Seven red flags that expose a grift before it hooks you
✨ How to trust your body’s cues as your first line of spiritual defense
